## Complete User Journey with All Systems

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    Start([User visits Foundrly]) --> Load[Load Application]
    
    Load --> Auth{User Authenticated?}
    Auth -->|No| Guest[Guest Experience]
    Auth -->|Yes| LoggedIn[Logged In Experience]
    
